# LearnHub API Structure

The API module follows a standard Spring Boot structure with controllers, services, and supporting components.

## Controller Layout
The API endpoints are divided into backend (admin) and frontend (student) controllers:

### Backend Controllers
- [Backend Controllers](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-api/src/main/java/xyz/learnhub/api/controller/backend) - Admin management interfaces
  - [AdminUserController](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-api/src/main/java/xyz/learnhub/api/controller/backend/AdminUserController.java) - Administrator management
  - [CourseController](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-api/src/main/java/xyz/learnhub/api/controller/backend/CourseController.java) - Course management
  - [DepartmentController](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-api/src/main/java/xyz/learnhub/api/controller/backend/DepartmentController.java) - Department management
  - [ResourceController](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-api/src/main/java/xyz/learnhub/api/controller/backend/ResourceController.java) - Resource management
  - [UserController](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-api/src/main/java/xyz/learnhub/api/controller/backend/UserController.java) - User management

### Frontend Controllers
- [Frontend Controllers](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-api/src/main/java/xyz/learnhub/api/controller/frontend) - Student-facing endpoints
  - [LoginController](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-api/src/main/java/xyz/learnhub/api/controller/frontend/LoginController.java) - Student login
  - [CourseController](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-api/src/main/java/xyz/learnhub/api/controller/frontend/CourseController.java) - Course access

## API Application Components
- [LearnHubApiApplication](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-api/src/main/java/xyz/learnhub/api/LearnHubApiApplication.java) - Main application entry point
- [Request DTOs](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-api/src/main/java/xyz/learnhub/api/request) - Data transfer objects for API requests
- [Response Format](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-common/src/main/java/xyz/learnhub/common/util/JsonResponse.java) - Standard JSON response format
- [Event Handlers](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-api/src/main/java/xyz/learnhub/api/event) - Event-driven components
- [Scheduled Tasks](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-api/src/main/java/xyz/learnhub/api/schedule) - Scheduled/recurring tasks
- [Interceptors](mdc:learnhub-api/learnhub-api/src/main/java/xyz/learnhub/api/interceptor) - HTTP request interceptors
